   "endLine": 540,
   "source": "<ROUTINE IN-POOL-2-F (RARG)\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? .RARG ,M-LOOK>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"You are swimming underwater. In the darkness, you can't make out your\nsurroundings here.\">\n\t\t<COND (<LIT? ,ON-POOL-2>\n\t\t       <TELL\n\" However you do notice a faint light above you.\">)>\n\t\t<RTRUE>\n\t       ;<CRLF>)>>"
